snippet.title: Warside - Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
Warside is coming to Kickstarter! Choose your Commander, assemble your forces, and battle your way to victory. Follow on Kickstarter: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/lavabird/warside-a-pixel-art-turn-based-tactics-game

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2368300/Warside/
More details & Presskit: https://playwarside.com
Discord: https://discord.gg/SExEcArMca
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/PlayWarside
